long_description: The no-nonsense Freestyle Predator Watch features all the usual fitness elements in addition to a user-friendly pacer function, ideal for paddle-sports training. Pacer function features preset values ranging from 40 to 160 beeps per min. Dual time; date; alarm. Countdown timer; stopwatch; 10-lap memory. The Freestyle Predator Watch features a rugged case that resists water down to 100m (330 ft.); comfortable and durable nylon wristband.
